MOS Capacitor¶

Below are several plots for an NMOS-transistor in the threshold region ($n_{surface} = p_{bulk}$) for several temperatures. The oxide-bandgap is not to scale.

The default parameters are:

  • $N_A$ = 1e23 / m$^3$
  • $C_{ox}$ = 0.005755 F/m$^2$

mdl.temp = 30
v_gb = np.linspace(0, 10, 200)

mdl2 = mdl.copy_mdl(DiracQVcpp)
psis = mdl.psi_s(v_ch=0, v_gb=v_gb)
Q_m = mdl.Q_m(psi_s=psis, v_ch=0)

psis2= mdl2.psi_s(v_ch=0, v_gb=v_gb)
Q_m2= mdl2.Q_m(psi_s=psis2, v_ch=0)

plt.figure()
plt.plot(v_gb, -Q_m, 'b')
plt.plot(v_gb, -Q_m2, 'r')
plt.plot(v_gb, mdl.cox * (v_gb - mdl.v_th_d(4*mdl.phi_t)), 'k--')
plt.grid(), plt.xlabel("$V_{GB}$ (V)")
plt.show()
